name: mapreduce.job.encrypted-intermediate-data-key-size-bits
description: Mapreduce encrypt data key size default is 128

name: ipc.client.connect.retry.interval
description:
Indicates the number of milliseconds a client will wait for
    before retrying to establish a server connection.

name: seq.io.sort.mb
dfs.qjournal.parallel-read.num-threads
description: Number of threads per JN to be used for tailing edits.

name: dfs.storage.policy.satisfier.self.retry.timeout.millis
description:
If any of file related block movements not at all reported by datanode,
    then after this timeout(in milliseconds), the item will be added back to movement needed list
    at namenode which will be retried for block movements.
    The default value is 5 * 60 * 1000 (5 mins)

name: dfs.blockreport.initialDelay
description:
Delay for first block report in seconds. Support multiple time unit
    suffix(case insensitive), as described in dfs.heartbeat.interval.If
    no time unit is specified then seconds is assumed
